defaultProfessor Sir Brian Hoskinsdefault: Absolutely, and I agree that that is the case and it is interesting that the number of extremes in this last period have exposed our vulnerability to our environment. I will not get into the extent to which climate change is involved in this. However, it has certainly exposed—
